-- Cisco says gaining market share against rivals
-- 
-- Tue May 8, 2007 7:29pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/08/us-cisco-competitors-idUSWEN785420070508

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Cisco Systems Inc. ( CSCO.O ) Chief Executive John Chambers said on Tuesday the network equipment company was gaining market share from its competitors. 

 He also said in a conference call following the announcement of its fiscal third quarter results that momentum remained "very strong."